Class SearchableList.SearchableDisplayAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.widget.BaseAdapter
      • android.widget.ArrayAdapter
        • com.example.lab_net.SearchableList.SearchableDisplayAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.widget.Adapter, android.widget.Filterable, android.widget.ListAdapter, android.widget.SpinnerAdapter, android.widget.ThemedSpinnerAdapter
    Enclosing class:
    SearchableList

    private class SearchableList.SearchableDisplayAdapter
extends android.widget.ArrayAdapter
    A SearchableDisplayAdapter is the general class that will handle all searchables and put them into a displayable form. This is done by finding the appropriate ListDisplayAdapterSegment and deferring control to it to create the View.
